highlights.text: “ไฟเย็น” by YOUNGOHM has been on Top Songs Thailand the longest, at 972 days straight.
YOUNGOHM has the most spots on Top Songs Thailand. “นครดารา” is the highest at #6.
“ปิดตาข้างนึง” by Song Thai is the highest new entry on Top Songs Thailand at #199.
“ธรรมดา” by DIAMOND MQT is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Thailand, up 81 spots at #78.
